Package com.teamviewer.sdk.screensharing.api

Contains interfaces and classes for interacting with the TeamViewer Screen sharing SDK.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TVSession
    Represents a session created with TVSessionFactory.createTVSession(Activity, String, TVSessionCreationCallback) and provides operations on it.
    TVSessionCallback
    Callback to be supplied to TVSession.setTVSessionCallback(TVSessionCallback).
    TVSessionCreationCallback
    Callback to be supplied to TVSessionFactory.createTVSession(Activity, String, TVSessionCreationCallback).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TVConfigurationID
    Immutable representation of a configuration ID.
    TVDebugTools
    Utility class for collecting log files or sending these to the TeamViewer support.
    TVSessionCode
    Immutable representation of a session code.
    TVSessionConfiguration
    Configuration options for starting a TVSession.
    TVSessionConfiguration.Builder
    Builder for creating an immutable TVSessionConfiguration.
    TVSessionFactory
    Factory for creating new sessions.
    TVSessionService
    Service that keeps the app process alive and displays a notification.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TVCreationError
    Enumeration of errors, which can happen during session creation.
    TVSessionError
    Enumeration of errors, which can happen during a session.
